<L>__{interior hill house front doors, entry early morning}
<A>__{the house inhales. and boom! the front doors blast wide. every door in the entry slams open.}
<L>__{exterior hill house early morning}
<A>__{against the early light of a rising sun, the silhouette of hill house. every window and every door in the house is open, each and every one crying out with a different, unintelligible voice, like a soul, the soul of a child, escaping from each one.}
